  analyst_note = '2026 SPAC merger via Bleichroeder Acquisition Corp II at 2.6B$ pro forma. 200M$ convertible round closed 2026 led by Inflection Point and Bpifrance. CA growth ~100% in 2025. Backlog of 80M$ in firm contracts and grants. Cash position 158M$ Feb 2026. Real industrial customers including CMA CGM, NVIDIA and BMW. Competitive edge: neutral atom approach more stable at room temperature than competing modalities.',
